reviewText: This was another Christmas gift for my husband. We enjoyed watching Mama's Family in the past so I know we will just love it now.
I was unaware that this video contained only 6 episodes.  The episodes on this video weren't very good, so I was extremely disappointed.
We've enjoyed a lots of laughs & fun. Mama is a good comedy with mostly clean fun. I highly recommend.
Color/sound great. Stories wonderful. DVD plays as if show just recorded. Sorry there weren't more shows. Delivery was quick/good packaging.
